beer.beer_description:
An homage to a Belgian classic, made with orange peel and coriander seeds as tradition dictates.

Resting on a soft foundation provided by the yeast, you get the pithy taste from the orange peel combined with the subtle character of the spices. Refreshing and crisp, while staying calm.
